{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c342569bf2","title":"给毛爱桂的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"851451206a","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"c342569bf2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"c3cc9cf31d","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛爱桂，1914年生，湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶山村人，农民。毛泽东的族叔。"},{"id":"39da513359","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"爱棠，即毛爱堂（1895—1927）。1925年赴广州参加革命，曾为广东省中共党组织工作人员。1927年在湖北武昌辆性。"},{"id":"f9c866f07f","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李远明（1895-1951），湖南省韶山市永义乡狮山村人，毛爱桂的姐夫。毛泽东在长沙读书和在韶山开展农民运动时，李家曾给予资助。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7de7aab5e2","type":"title","text":"给毛爱柱的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"},{"id":"c3cc9cf31d","type":"paragraph","text":"爱桂先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"},{"id":"39da513359","type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到。令兑爱棠叫于一九二六年参加北伐军，在广东曾见过一面，以后即未见过。有人说已性了，极为可惜。这是为国性，是光荣的。此复，并候合家清吉！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"},{"id":"f9c866f07f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"},{"id":"69d0fc759e","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年五月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"},{"id":"b680ed5f51","type":"paragraph","text":"李远明先生同此不另","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2"}],"page":{"id":"6ad3a38763","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"c342569bf2","start":381,"end":381}}}},"__N_SSG":true}